{"results":[{"aya":"015","id":5462,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"至於乖张的，将作火狱的燃料。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"016","id":5463,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"假如他们遵循正道，我必赏赐他们的丰富的雨水，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"017","id":5464,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"以便我以雨水考验他们。谁退避主的教训，他将使谁入在严峻的刑罚中。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"018","id":5465,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"一切清真寺，都是真主的，故你们应当祈祷真主，不要祈祷任何物。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"019","id":5466,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"当真主的仆人起来祈祷的时候，他们几乎群起而攻之。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"020","id":5467,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"你说：我只祈祷我的主，我不以任何物配他。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"021","id":5468,"locale":"zh","sura":"072","text":"你说：我不能为你们主持祸福。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":4,"previousPage":"/zh/s072-2.json","nextPage":"/zh/s072-4.json"}}